source.name: Average Wait Time Until Hearing Held Report (formerly NETSTAT Report)
source.description: A presentation of the average time (in months) from the hearing request date until a hearing is held for claims pending in the Office of Disability Adjudication and Review's hearing offices.  Allows users to estimate the amount  of time they may have to wait for a hearing to be held.
